SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
------------------
1) clone
2) bundle install
3) rake db:create
4) rake db:migrate
5) rake db:fixtures:load
6) rails s -p 3000
7) http://localhost:3000/account/signup/
8) Create a user.  First user created is the admin.

OLD SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
----------------------
Refer to /doc/INSTALL for setup instructions.

